        "---\n",
        "title: Jupyter + Stata 配置方法\n",
        "subtitle: VS Code 或 JupyterLab Desktop｜对 Windows 10 用户适用，时效截至 2024 年\n",
        "description: 对文科生友好\n",
        "abstract: 暂无\n",
        "author: 刘景山\n",
        "date: \"2024-4-28\"\n",
        "categories: [操作经验,Jupyter,Stata]\n",
        "number-sections: true\n",
